data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful end-unit town home.  This is the former builder's model so there are lots of upgrades.  At 2100+ square feet, this home is sure to impress.  Stately washed brick front greats you as you pull into your 4 car driveway. Upon entering this home, you will notice the fireplace located in the family room.  Upgraded recess lighting, wood mantle, wainscoting, and a sliding patio door complete the family room.  Speaking of Patio door, look out onto the covered 18x18 patio and the private rear yard.  No neighbors looking back at you as it back to private space.  The once car built-in garage and powder room complete the first floor.  The upper floor consists of the Kitchen with Stainless Steel appliance package, under cabinet lighting and ample storage space.  There is a kitchen island along with plenty of room for a formal dining room or just a kitchen table. The sliding patio doors lead out to a 16x16 Trex deck with privacy fencing.  It also overlooks the private rear yard.  The is  more upgraded recess lighting and the wainscoting continues in the kitchen and dining room.   The living room boasts 3 large windows for plenty of natural light, Brazilian cherry hardwood floors and a custom brick wall along the entire front interior wall.   The 3rd level consists of the master bedroom with vaulted ceilings, a huge walk-in closet and of course the master bath.  The master bath has separate double sinks so you're not stepping over each other and a corner Jacuzzi tub along with a stand-up shower.  This is truly an owner's sanctuary.  Two other bedrooms and hall bath complete the third floor.  You have to see this home to appreciate it even more.  Call today for your private tour.
